### Variables comunes
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = PONER_TOKEN_JWT_AQUI

### Listar tarifas
GET {{baseUrl}}/tarifas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear tarifa
POST {{baseUrl}}/tarifas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

